    "description": "CGeNArateWeb is a web server for simulating the structure and dynamics of chromatin fibers using a coarse-grained Hamiltonian. The server allows users to obtain simulations of DNA, including linear, circular, and protein-DNA segments, and to analyze the results using a set of nucleic acid-specific tools.",
